Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Are you a granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is this "granny classroom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.31,Housei,,0,0,0,,If so, you'll get a full score on it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:54.41,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Are you in charge of this?
