Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's not it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We already have one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.57,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Actually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I heard that he disappeared without explanations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.21,Housei,,0,0,0,,But really, I wonder what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.66,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,614)}I want to know
