Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you want to show us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:33.77,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\pos(834,430)}Michael Jackson Classroom - Third Lesson:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:33.77,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\c&H1EF1EA&\pos(820,524)}Learn his attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:33.39,Others,,0,0,0,,Next up is a training to become like Michael on a mental side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:43.21,Upper Notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(612,580)}Please, do not expect much from today's episode
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:43.21,Upper Notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H00&\pos(604,630)}nothing in particular is going to happen overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.30,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Listen, let's just stop moving around for now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.76,Murakami,,0,0,0,,We're all tired, let's set it aside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.02,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Let's do a Michael training using our head, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:44.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.91,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'm now going to show you some of Michael's famous pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.24,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Let's make it like a quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.59,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'll give a prize to whoever gets it right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.25,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.31,Murakami,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.58,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Do you know this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's his signature pose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:05.23,Housei,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the "POH" we just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,622)}Oh right, that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.23,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,622)}It's the "POH"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.00,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Not even close
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.86,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a hint, he was in Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.64,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It's like he's saying "so spicy!", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.61,Endo,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was eating Jjigae?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Something spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.61,Murakami,,0,0,0,,No, it's not Jjigae!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Kimchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.54,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,628)}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.31,Murakami,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:23.28,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It was a home-made Kimchi made by a korean mom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's saying something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.92,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Something like "WOOOOOOW!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,And that means "it's spicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:29.82,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You won something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.92,Murakami,,0,0,0,,You're weak, so I'm giving you this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.26,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Take it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.19,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Try to hold this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.86,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Hold it tight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.84,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}that{\i0} banana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.50,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.51,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I got this from Mah-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:50.18,Upper Notes,,0,0,0,,note: Masahiro Tanaka, baseball player
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.18,Endo,,0,0,0,,You mean Masahiro Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.14,Murakami,,0,0,0,,A guy who works in a yakitori shop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.70,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Not our Mah-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.38,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright, next one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.71,Endo,,0,0,0,,He liked kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.54,Murakami,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.41,Murakami,,0,0,0,,That's true, but this dude is not a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.12,Murakami,,0,0,0,,He's not a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's an old dude
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.16,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,618)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:08.88,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It's from an exhibition in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.45,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1EF1EA&\3c&H000000&\4c&H1EF1EA&\4a&HA3&}An exhibition in Japan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:10.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.46,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's from the backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:17.60,Murakami,,0,0,0,,That's a picture from when he met Minoru Shiraki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:17.60,Upper Notes,,0,0,0,,note: a very short japanese actor (1,40m)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:20.04,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Such a shame none of you got it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.74,Murakami,,0,0,0,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is he spotting someone from the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.88,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Damn, you were so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.98,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Think about something he puts on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:30.48,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.15,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.58,Endo,,0,0,0,,Sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:32.58,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,612)}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:37.15,Murakami,,0,0,0,,He forgot his sunglasses, these are impromptu hand-sunglasses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.15,Murakami,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.12,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:47.50,Murakami,,0,0,0,,That's a hat I got from a hostess in Ebisu 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.30,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright, Matsumoto try harder ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You're right, I will
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.27,Murakami,,0,0,0,,This one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's the picture from when he met Minoru Shiraki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.64,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Oh, my mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.67,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Here, Matsumoto, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.87,Murakami,,0,0,0,,You got it right, so here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is...?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&}- A bag for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.58,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.75,Murakami,,0,0,0,,One more thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.32,Murakami,,0,0,0,,As an extra prize, I'll have you hold this, Matsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,610)}You had that too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.02,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's huge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.95,Murakami,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.55,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It's a movie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.89,Upper Notes,,0,0,0,,"Crow's thumb" by Tadafumi Ito, 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.18,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:16.89,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Coming out this fall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.89,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is this really coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.00,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.99,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is it a prop or is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.63,Murakami,,0,0,0,,No, this is real
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.33,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I have more if you want to see them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.53,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Like this one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:33.98,Housei,,0,0,0,,It seems so fake somehow...\N{\c&HF60919&}- What's with this pose?!\N{\c&H1A8CFF&}- You sure it's not a prop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I mean look at it, it looks so fake
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:36.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.12,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I swear it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.61,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's with this expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.32,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sort of the main character
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"Crow's thumb"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.09,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.32,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I also have this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.35,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Looks so fake though
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:52.35,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Is this true?    {\c&HF60919&} - You gotta be kidding me\N{\c&H22D727&}- It feels weird
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say about this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But it looks true
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.60,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'll bring this up again later
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.60,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'll go get em
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.46,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.56,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Next training
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:09.74,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\c&H000000&\pos(364,530)}Michael Jackson Classroom - Fourth Lesson:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:09.74,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&H88&\3a&H97&\c&H1EF1EA&\fnImpact\fs35\pos(336,600)}Learn his steps
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.90,Others,,0,0,0,,Here's their final training
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.50,Others,,0,0,0,,It's time to learn Michael's incredible steps
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.74,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I think it become clear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.41,Murakami,,0,0,0,,What to do with the third generation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N{\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&}- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.35,Murakami,,0,0,0,,But let me say this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.62,Murakami,,0,0,0,,You're not ready to be Michael Jackson yet, it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.48,Murakami,,0,0,0,,That's why I think I should show you Michael's greatness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.06,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Some more
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.33,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.19,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Take these
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He really likes those too...\N{\c&HF60919&}- True
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.47,Murakami,,0,0,0,,These are ash bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:43.47,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Back then when I used to live on the countryside
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.83,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I used to put ash inside bags and throw em
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.21,Murakami,,0,0,0,,To old dudes on the fields
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:48.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ash bombs?\N{\c&H1A8CFF&}- That's their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.38,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Yeah we called em like that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.34,Murakami,,0,0,0,,If they hit you, they cause some damage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.18,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Of course they do\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}- {\i1}If{\i0} they hit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.62,Murakami,,0,0,0,,But now I'm going to avoid em all while dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If he manages to do it he's even better than Michael, isn't him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.32,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:03.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.09,Endo,,0,0,0,,Woah, ash bombs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.76,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Throw em as they are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.79,Housei,,0,0,0,,Let us know when you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.76,Murakami,,0,0,0,,It's ok, throw em
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:36.46,Murakami,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,612)}I think that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.86,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.26,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:45.10,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll pay for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.30,Murakami,,0,0,0,,If it's money---
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.94,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294,392)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.37,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\fs56\pos(294,384)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.37,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.87,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:53.81,Murakami,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:55.73,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:01.65,Murakami,,0,0,0,,This is my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.01,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how it got there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.75,Murakami,,0,0,0,,THRILLER!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.28,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Thriller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't this--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:20.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's go home    {\c&H1A8CFF&}  - It's so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.87,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,622)}Macchan it's just like we said during the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He even shouted "thriller"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.41,Murakami,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,622)}You were laughing so much during our meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.61,Murakami,,0,0,0,,Endo! Come here and apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Enough
